            "title": "字符串的基本输出回顾",
            "content": "小李想打印一句问候语：\"Good morning\"。以下哪一项写法正确？",
            "options": {
                "A": "print(Good morning)",
                "B": "print(\"Good morning\")",
                "C": "echo(\"Good morning\")",
                "D": "print('Good morning')"
            },
            "answer": "B",
            "hints": [
                "Python 输出必须使用 print。",
                "字符串需要引号。",
                "注意区分 Python 语法与其他语言语法。"
            ],
            "explanation": "print(\"Good morning\") 是标准 Python 字符串输出。",
            "example": "你也可以输出 print(\"Have a nice day\") 来练习。"
        },
